# Compiled `go build` outputs of this module's main packages. Root-anchored so
# they never shadow like-named source dirs (cmd/weave-guestd) or the embedded
# agent assets (internal/guestweaveagent/agentbin/dist/weave-guestd-*).
#   .                                      -> weave (default) / guestweave (-o)
#   internal/acceptance                    -> acceptance
#   internal/guestweaveagent/cmd/weave-guestd -> weave-guestd
/weave
/guestweave
/acceptance
/weave-guestd
# ...and if built from inside their own package directories:
/internal/acceptance/acceptance
/internal/guestweaveagent/cmd/weave-guestd/weave-guestd
hvmmtest
